    <description># PDFCreator Professional 

## Features
- **PDFCreator Professional** is ad-free and includes priority support by e-mail.
- Can be used in combination with **HotFolder**. HotFolder allows to create special folders on any computer. Files added to these folders are automatically converted to PDF or image files.
- Includes a small tool called **Images2PDF**, which lets you convert images to PDF easily and quickly.
- **PDFCreator Professional** is an admin-friendly solution that allows easy unattended deployment. Group policies enable administrators to predefine specific settings centrally through the Active Directory.

## Setup Command Line Parameters
To add command line parameters to the installer, please use:
`--installer-arguments="[parameters]"`

The list of possible `parameters` can be found below:
- **/LicenseKey=`LicenseKey`**
- **/ProxyUsername=`ProxyUsername`**
- **/ProxyPassword=`ProxyPassword`**
- **/ProxyName=`ProxyName`** - `ProxyName:Port`
- **/Lang="en"** - List of two letter language codes
- **/Dir="X:\DIR\PDFCreator"** - Absolute path to desired installation directory
- **/NoIcons** - No icons created on the Desktop
- **/DisableContextMenu** - No entries in the context menu
- **/DisableStartMenu** - No entries in the start menu

PDFCreator is a very lightweight application. If your machine is able to run a modern Windows OS without troubles, it should be able to run PDFCreator. For more detailed instructions please see the [user guide](https://docs.pdfforge.org/pdfcreator/en/pdfcreator/installing-pdfcreator/setup-command-line-parameters/) 

